Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.71,0:00:11.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fight 不要回头
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.63,0:00:14.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fight 迈步出发
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.80,0:00:17.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼泪是闪闪发光的勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.80,0:00:20.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每一步 都化为甘霖
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.78,0:00:25.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fight Fight 更加自信了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.31,0:00:36.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不需要的东西就舍去 这样也好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.40,0:00:42.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在无限广阔的心中蔓延开来哟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.68,0:00:48.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于受伤时刻之外　看不见的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.73,0:00:54.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若现在开始映入双眸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.68,0:00:56.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Just Try-again
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.01,0:01:01.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变得强大 抓住机会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.00,0:01:07.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fight 无论何时
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.01,0:01:10.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fight 都要坚信
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.04,0:01:13.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梦想绝对能实现
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.13,0:01:16.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有多遥远 都不害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.13,0:01:22.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fight Fight 更能感觉到明天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.34,0:01:35.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫战部渡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.96,0:01:39.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了打倒支配了在遥远天空上的星界山的多坏达
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.91,0:01:44.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们以第七星界为目标展开了冒险旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.75,0:01:48.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在身处的是有趣西部的第五星界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.50,0:01:50.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打倒了以骗人道具做生意的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.97,0:01:53.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥加·金婆婆之后的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.17,0:01:55.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又再次向黑暗之幕进发了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.68,0:01:59.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天也会是"超"有趣又有型
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.78,0:02:08.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第三十一话\N黑暗来临电影之镇!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.27,0:02:24.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡,不如在这里休息一会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.37,0:02:27.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的,到底什么时候才能到山顶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.31,0:02:28.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在下也…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.71,0:02:31.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看,手也麻痹了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.95,0:02:37.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来到了一个麻烦的地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.32,0:02:40.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.42,0:02:43.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有市镇啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.13,0:02:50.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.61,0:02:51.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,累死了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.64,0:02:52.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.76,0:02:55.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边这边这边有个古怪的镇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.51,0:03:04.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确是古怪的镇呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.95,0:03:06.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅,去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.96,0:03:35.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是我们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.83,0:03:37.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.58,0:03:40.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底这个镇是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.85,0:03:45.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部都是我们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.85,0:03:46.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.96,0:03:50.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是我们的活跃拍成了电影
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.68,0:03:53.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果这样的话我便是主角…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.90,0:03:56.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然变成了电影明星
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.21,0:03:57.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不好意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.07,0:04:00.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果被围着签名便伤脑筋了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.64,0:04:02.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不如立刻去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.58,0:04:03.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.44,0:04:04.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂,渡!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.97,0:04:06.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看这一套吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.08,0:04:14.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像现在刚开始呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.94,0:04:25.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很期待呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.03,0:04:34.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开火!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.48,0:04:42.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.43,0:04:59.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.26,0:05:00.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么一回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.50,0:05:02.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是说明星
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.82,0:05:05.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样我们不是成了死角吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.59,0:05:18.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还想看多点呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.43,0:05:21.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡,这个镇很奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.38,0:05:22.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.03,0:05:23.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.01,0:05:29.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.39,0:05:33.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们全部都是坏人吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.26,0:05:34.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好有型啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.81,0:05:36.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正式拍摄了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.31,0:05:51.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.37,0:05:55.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"渡杀掉所有人大作战 part2"要拍了!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.38,0:05:56.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.13,0:06:08.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是用真枪好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.99,0:06:12.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我奥斯卡导演大人的多坏达电影
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.71,0:06:15.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都有真实的迫力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.70,0:06:16.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停手!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.26,0:06:20.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊,你是渡!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.04,0:06:24.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对镇内的居民做这么过分的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.30,0:06:25.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是不会原谅的!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.85,0:06:29.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我们拍成死角的电影的人便是你吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.22,0:06:30.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.14,0:06:35.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把你们拍成死角的电影上映
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.15,0:06:39.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是伟也绽·奥里零大人的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.29,0:06:40.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.58,0:06:41.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有一件事…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.69,0:06:45.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是一发现通缉犯渡便立刻消灭!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.67,0:06:47.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅,好!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.52,0:06:55.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在正式拍摄了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.28,0:06:59.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来会拍出好场面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.39,0:07:10.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才真危险呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.26,0:07:11.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你,师傅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.66,0:07:13.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混帐,钢铁兵们!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.12,0:07:16.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以让他们有命回去!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.60,0:07:21.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是吃早餐前的爆谷和汽水
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.67,0:07:24.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还是死心投降吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.54,0:07:27.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的剧情剧本上是没有的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.82,0:07:31.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是,这种事对导演是不通用的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.62,0:07:37.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了呢,师傅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.95,0:07:39.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们合力的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.97,0:07:41.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,便是天下无敌的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.16,0:07:45.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大叔,下次我也要拍啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.07,0:07:55.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救世主渡吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.64,0:08:04.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,电影之都荷里布活?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.44,0:08:05.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.71,0:08:10.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前这个荷里布活市是人们的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.70,0:08:13.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人们憧憬的电影都市
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.63,0:08:22.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.52,0:08:28.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在变成了为了奥斯卡导演
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.45,0:08:31.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拍多坏达电影的市镇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.74,0:08:33.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是这样吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.22,0:08:34.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶的导演
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.25,0:08:35.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能饶恕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.44,0:08:38.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起此事,黑暗世界已迫近!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.48,0:08:40.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家快些逃吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.51,0:08:45.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是,我们的同伴还在导演那里被迫工作
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.65,0:08:47.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能留下他们逃走的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.02,0:08:50.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些人由我们去救吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.66,0:08:51.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧,师傅!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.93,0:08:54.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯,放心交给我们吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.63,0:08:56.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交给我们吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.75,0:09:22.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,导演,黑暗世界已接近了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.79,0:09:25.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好,差不多时候来正式的了!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.13,0:09:27.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.97,0:09:35.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我奥斯卡导演的最新作
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.64,0:09:40.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"沉默的到来,13号的黑暗世界"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.24,0:09:44.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你们见识到黑暗的可怕力量
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.85,0:09:48.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种恐怖感太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.52,0:09:49.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唔?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.25,0:09:50.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.19,0:09:57.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混帐,渡!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.89,0:09:59.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位,我们来救你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.71,0:10:03.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,野牛武一郎流,交叉字斩!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.10,0:10:08.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了各位,快逃吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.57,0:10:13.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混帐!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.81,0:10:16.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会就这样让你们有命回去的!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.45,0:10:23.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.78,0:10:24.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.65,0:10:29.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们就这样被卷入黑暗世界之中吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.26,0:10:35.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡啊,怎样做才好?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.23,0:11:15.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,形状虽然怪,但那是市镇吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.58,0:11:18.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有趣,去看一看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.28,0:11:19.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧,山昂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.98,0:11:30.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.77,0:11:33.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去会被吞进黑暗世界的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.11,0:11:37.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已来到这么近了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.33,0:11:42.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救世主也到此为止了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.19,0:11:45.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是,就这样的话不有趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.21,0:11:55.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.21,0:11:57.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不知道是什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.68,0:11:59.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之好像得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.32,0:12:01.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还在想不知会变成怎样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.06,0:12:02.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混帐!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.06,0:12:04.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话就用这个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.38,0:12:07.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.06,0:12:07.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.24,0:12:11.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带上这个分割面具的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.29,0:12:14.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定会变成自己人打自己人的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.23,0:12:15.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去了!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.99,0:12:24.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又再失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.37,0:12:30.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于变得有趣了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.46,0:12:31.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么再加一把
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.85,0:12:42.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧?渡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.03,0:12:47.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡的样子很怪!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.98,0:12:52.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知为何分割面具复活了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.74,0:12:53.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.41,0:12:56.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡,对付你的同伴吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.20,0:12:57.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂,渡…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.60,0:13:00.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡!怪,怪,怪!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.28,0:13:06.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很有型呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.72,0:13:15.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样了,和我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.59,0:13:18.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最新作的构思太适合了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.73,0:13:20.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就请这样子继续
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.36,0:13:22.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样便行了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.58,0:13:25.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好,前无去路!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.36,0:13:27.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请救我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.09,0:13:30.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪的脸!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.63,0:13:31.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.56,0:13:34.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想法子取去那个面具的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.98,0:13:39.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多是时候玩完了,渡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.11,0:13:42.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能以剑交锋吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.42,0:13:46.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.16,0:13:55.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊,鸟先生啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.19,0:13:56.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.75,0:14:00.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已除掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.08,0:14:02.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我到底…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.02,0:14:06.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来已清醒了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.46,0:14:08.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古拿玛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.59,0:14:10.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很久没见了,渡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.18,0:14:11.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你来到正好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.01,0:14:14.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸟先生,你去干什么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.50,0:14:15.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有很多事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.80,0:14:18.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一时间我还不知怎办
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.13,0:14:20.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是发了一场恶梦一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.52,0:14:24.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又有型又令人感动四人的重逢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.22,0:14:26.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是自然式的友情…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.49,0:14:27.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.45,0:14:30.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什么时候变成了青春电影?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.90,0:14:34.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我难得到新作的大场面出场了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.10,0:14:36.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死亡剪片!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.05,0:14:50.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡,这里交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.35,0:14:51.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.76,0:15:00.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙星丸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.47,0:15:46.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你知道死亡剪片的厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.57,0:15:48.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摄影机准备好了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.80,0:15:49.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.49,0:15:52.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始摄影!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.08,0:15:55.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去了,渡!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.16,0:15:55.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.65,0:16:04.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一点本事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.67,0:16:07.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙星丸,给他看看力量的差别
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.38,0:16:08.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.36,0:16:13.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还未完!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.67,0:16:22.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙星丸,一口气收拾他!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.91,0:16:23.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.31,0:16:28.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混帐!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.27,0:16:30.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,离完场还早啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.78,0:16:32.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接接看吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.32,0:16:45.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓片爪!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.43,0:16:50.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙星丸,加油!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.14,0:16:52.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯,这些爪算得上什么!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.47,0:16:54.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要逞强了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.38,0:17:03.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来能拍出最棒的结局场面了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.98,0:17:06.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙星丸的死期
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.69,0:17:17.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从正中间分开两边
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.40,0:17:22.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直被缚着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.17,0:17:25.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,便不能避开那电锯了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.15,0:17:25.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吓!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.61,0:17:32.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不解开这些爪不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.70,0:17:33.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办?渡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.35,0:17:36.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了,用超天空幻龙波吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.90,0:17:39.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要解脱这些爪的话只有这一招了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.55,0:17:41.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是不知道能否顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.18,0:17:42.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有试一试了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.55,0:17:43.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.66,0:17:47.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超天空幻龙波!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.14,0:18:00.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危险!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.81,0:18:04.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的电影底片啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.33,0:18:05.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是时候了,渡!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.06,0:18:06.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.18,0:18:10.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光龙剑!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.93,0:18:27.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必杀!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.60,0:18:30.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光龙剑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.08,0:18:47.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是大团圆结局呢!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.66,0:18:56.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,市镇变得黑黑了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.03,0:19:00.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去第五星界便会完全变成黑暗世界了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.63,0:19:02.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想办法的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.50,0:19:03.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.88,0:19:04.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.10,0:19:05.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海火子!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.47,0:19:08.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在这里干什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.69,0:19:10.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是,为什么会在这里的?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.04,0:19:12.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事什么也不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.21,0:19:14.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倒是你要怎么办?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.71,0:19:17.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在不是一步也不能前进了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.38,0:19:20.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.60,0:19:31.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是谁!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.53,0:19:35.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的名字叫加麾斯利路
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.60,0:19:37.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加麾斯利路?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.62,0:19:41.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道驱除那黑暗的方法吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.06,0:19:43.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要驱除这黑暗的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.98,0:19:46.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,便要用圣天界的神圣之火
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.36,0:19:51.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燃点在黑暗中心的光之女神像的松明
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.50,0:19:52.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣天界?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.97,0:19:56.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个圣天界要怎样才能去到?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.94,0:20:00.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣天界的入口已在黑暗里面了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.21,0:20:01.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎会的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.34,0:20:03.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么便去不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.28,0:20:05.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我便驱走黑暗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.89,0:20:06.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吓?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.88,0:20:45.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个便是唯一能通往圣天界的入口
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.97,0:20:47.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣天门
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.06,0:20:52.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.42,0:20:56.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣天界是超越你们想像的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.23,0:20:58.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许会有不知道的危险在等着你们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.20,0:21:02.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然我不能保证你们会有命回来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.20,0:21:03.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果这样你们也要去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.02,0:21:05.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是不会阻止的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.14,0:21:08.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅,去圣天界吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.48,0:21:10.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我们的力量集合的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.35,0:21:12.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不论遇上什么事也没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.25,0:21:13.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.42,0:21:14.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.29,0:21:15.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也跟你去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.72,0:21:17.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"我们"是什么意思啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.96,0:21:19.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也要去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.39,0:21:23.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好,大家去圣天界吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.88,0:21:24.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.81,0:21:38.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好,去吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.30,0:21:39.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.37,0:21:51.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向圣天界进发的救世主渡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.91,0:21:52.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.90,0:21:54.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要怎样做?多坏达
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.39,0:22:07.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣天界…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.63,0:22:09.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是个怎样的地方?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.94,0:22:37.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在 阴霾的天空里乌云渐渐散去 阳光透过云层照了下来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.51,0:22:47.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两个人仰望这天空的哪个角落
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.63,0:22:53.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眩目的彩虹 即将出来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.36,0:22:54.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,注定出来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.18,0:22:58.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快走吧 奔跑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.81,0:23:02.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁着光线还没有消失的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.24,0:23:09.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,期待着明天的幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.39,0:23:12.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快走吧 奔跑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.97,0:23:16.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,熠熠生辉的彩虹彼岸里
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.38,0:23:24.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吹出了两个人未来的风

